replies.body:
Hey Dartwolf 5664, 

I wouldn't worry about it to much unless you are intentionally feeding, or not helping. (Which seems to not be the case) We can't be perfect at this game, and some games will be better than others. Try to keep your head up and don't let toxic people ruin the game for you. Instead focus on becoming better with each game and if you have to mute the toxic players do it. You don't need to deal with people flaming you because you're having an off game. Do your best and keep up the awesome work :) 

